snippet.textDisplay:
My take on this wonderful song:-
Malevoice- Yearning to express his love, failed at a few attempts, and almost gave in  just because his love being unresponsive from the other sides, the eternal sufferings of waiting.

Femalevoice- Quite unsure about the other side of love, waiting for the moment to get a call, an unfinished love story that was yet to happen, 

Male + Female- Still hoping to rejoin, an eternal connection (Male), Heard the callings from other side, pure but ambiguous (Female)  

Surely the title suits best  "long distance love"
It's like a one-sided distant love story, yet the emotions are relentless and come from both sides.
